WEBVTT

00:00:00.902 --> 00:00:03.333
Svo vreme grešimo.

00:00:04.379 --> 00:00:05.529
Svi.

00:00:05.960 --> 00:00:07.351
Sve vreme grešimo.

00:00:08.508 --> 00:00:10.594
Poslednje što bi trebalo da radimo

00:00:11.515 --> 00:00:12.782
jeste da čistimo okean.

00:00:14.054 --> 00:00:15.229
Poslednje.

00:00:16.007 --> 00:00:18.985
Da, po jedan đubretarski kamion plastike

00:00:20.166 --> 00:00:21.366
završi u okeanu

00:00:22.125 --> 00:00:23.275
svakog minuta

00:00:23.807 --> 00:00:25.540
svakog sata u svakom danu.

00:00:27.180 --> 00:00:29.299
I nebrojene ptice i životinje

00:00:29.323 --> 00:00:31.791
umiru samo od susreta sa plastikom.